{
  "name": "OpenCodex",
  "dsl": {
    "schema": "2.0",
    "config": {
      "update_multi": true,
      "streaming_mode": true,
      "streaming_config": {
        "print_step": {
          "default": 2,
          "pc": 4,
          "mobile": 2
        },
        "print_frequency_ms": {
          "default": 80,
          "pc": 60,
          "mobile": 100
        },
        "print_strategy": "fast"
      },
      "summary": {
        "content": "OpenCodex 正在生成中"
      }
    },
    "header": {
      "title": {
        "tag": "plain_text",
        "content": "OpenCodex"
      },
      "subtitle": {
        "tag": "plain_text",
        "content": "Codex / Terminal / Math Unified Card"
      },
      "text_tag_list": [
        {
          "tag": "text_tag",
          "text": {
            "tag": "plain_text",
            "content": "LIVE"
          },
          "color": "blue"
        },
        {
          "tag": "text_tag",
          "text": {
            "tag": "plain_text",
            "content": "STREAM"
          },
          "color": "wathet"
        },
        {
          "tag": "text_tag",
          "text": {
            "tag": "plain_text",
            "content": "OpenCodex"
          },
          "color": "indigo"
        }
      ],
      "template": "blue",
      "padding": "12px"
    },
    "body": {
      "direction": "vertical",
      "padding": "12px 12px 12px 12px",
      "vertical_spacing": "8px",
      "horizontal_align": "left",
      "vertical_align": "top",
      "elements": [
        {
          "tag": "column_set",
          "flex_mode": "stretch",
          "horizontal_align": "left",
          "margin": "0px",
          "columns": [
            {
              "tag": "column",
              "width": "weighted",
              "weight": 1,
              "background_style": "grey-50",
              "padding": "12px 12px 12px 12px",
              "vertical_spacing": "8px",
              "horizontal_align": "left",
              "vertical_align": "top",
              "elements": [
                {
                  "tag": "markdown",
                  "content": "### Activity"
                },
                {
                  "tag": "markdown",
                  "content": "${status_content}",
                  "text_align": "left",
                  "text_size": "normal",
                  "element_id": "status_content"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tag": "hr",
          "margin": "0px"
        },
        {
          "tag": "column_set",
          "flex_mode": "stretch",
          "horizontal_align": "left",
          "margin": "0px",
          "columns": [
            {
              "tag": "column",
              "width": "weighted",
              "weight": 1,
              "padding": "12px 12px 12px 12px",
              "vertical_spacing": "8px",
              "horizontal_align": "left",
              "vertical_align": "top",
              "elements": [
                {
                  "tag": "markdown",
                  "content": "### Response"
                },
                {
                  "tag": "markdown",
                  "content": "${answer_content}",
                  "text_align": "left",
                  "text_size": "normal",
                  "element_id": "answer_content"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tag": "hr",
          "margin": "0px"
        },
        {
          "tag": "column_set",
          "flex_mode": "stretch",
          "horizontal_align": "left",
          "margin": "0px",
          "columns": [
            {
              "tag": "column",
              "width": "weighted",
              "weight": 1,
              "background_style": "blue-50",
              "padding": "10px 12px 10px 12px",
              "vertical_spacing": "4px",
              "horizontal_align": "left",
              "vertical_align": "top",
              "elements": [
                {
                  "tag": "markdown",
                  "content": "**OpenCodex Message Card**\n适用于 Codex 会话、系统消息、数学辅导三类场景。回答区支持 Markdown、列表、引用、链接与代码块；状态区适合流式展示执行轨迹、完成状态与中断提示。"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  "variables": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "apiName": "var_mmxeth4g",
      "name": "answer_content",
      "desc": "OpenCodex 回答内容，支持 Markdown 富文本渲染。",
      "mockData": "### Response\n已连接到 OpenCodex 富文本卡片。\n\n- 支持 Markdown 标题\n- 支持列表\n- 支持引用\n- 支持代码块\n\n```shell\npython -m py_compile app.py\n```\n\n> 这是一条示例引用，用于验证飞书卡片中的富文本渲染效果。"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "apiName": "var_mmxethaa",
      "name": "status_content",
      "desc": "OpenCodex 状态内容，适合流式渲染执行轨迹。",
      "mockData": "1. 新请求已接收\n2. 正在分析项目结构\n3. 正在执行命令：`python -m py_compile app.py`\n4. 正在生成回答"
    }
  ]
}
